          <div class="tooltiptext-author"><div class="author-tooltip-affiliation"><span class="author-tooltip-text"> <div class="author-affiliation"><div class="affiliation-para"><ul><li class="aff"><a id="aff-1" name="aff-1"><!--nul--></a><address><sup>*</sup>Departments of Internal Medicine and </address></li></ul></div><div class='author-degree'>MD</div></div></span></div><ul class="author-tooltip-find-more"><li class="author-tooltip-gs-link"><a href="/lookup/google-scholar?link_type=googlescholar&gs_type=author&author=Kodlipet+C.+Dharmashankar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title= "Open in new tab">Find this author on Google Scholar</a></li><li class="author-tooltip-pubmed-link"><a href="/lookup/external-ref?apath=/clinmedres/8/1/1.atom&link_type=AUTHORSEARCH&access_num=Dharmashankar KC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find this author on PubMed</a></li><li class="author-site-search-link"><a href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-abs_connect?return_req=no_params&author=Dharmashankar%2C+K.+C&db_key=PRE&arxiv_sel=gr-qc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Find this author on ADS search</a></li><li class="author-tooltip-search-link"><a href="/search/?author1=Kodlipet C. Dharmashankar">Search for this author on this site</a></li></ul></div>
      </div>
